This repo has utilities and an IRC chat bot for getting information from
the world of warcraft API. As far as I know, the only API available is
getting realm status but once they add more I'll add more here.

Requirements
* JDK 1.6 or higher
* Maven 2.2.1

How to build
% mvn package

How to run the WowBot for IRC
% java -jar [jarfile] --hostname irc.host.com --channel #wow --port 6667 --username wowbot

Wowbot commands
* Realm Status
    wowbot: rs crushridge
    Realm{name='Crushridge', type=pvp, queue=false, status=true, slug='crushridge', population=medium}

